'''Quang Trung Software Park''' ({{lang-vi|Công viên phần mềm Quang Trung}}), also known as '''Quang Trung Software City''', is a [[business park]] in [[District 12, Ho Chi Minh City|District 12]] of [[Ho Chi Minh City]], approximately {{convert|15|km|mi}} from [[District 1, Ho Chi Minh City|District 1]]. The park focuses on the [[computer software]] industry, hosting a number of software companies and schools such as the [[Saigon Institute of Technology]]. Established by government decree in June 2000, it officially began operations on 16 March 2001.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.quangtrungsoft.com.vn/index.php/en/about-qtsc/who-we-are |title=Archived copy |accessdate=December 28, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100923205415/http://www.quangtrungsoft.com.vn/index.php/en/about-qtsc/who-we-are |archivedate=September 23, 2010 }}</ref>

